# Paths the `tauri dev` file-watcher must IGNORE (gitignore syntax).
#
# target/ is written by any manual `cargo check`/`cargo build` run with the
# default target dir. dev.bat builds into CARGO_TARGET_DIR=<drive>:\t, so the
# watcher doesn't ignore src-tauri/target automatically — and every manual
# cargo run then reads as thousands of "source changes", making tauri dev
# kill + rebuild + relaunch the app in a loop (seen 2026-07-04: an evening of
# phantom "crashes" and dead hotkeys that were really watcher churn).
target
logs
